2. SOURCE AVAILABILITY
   The source code in this repository is published for transparency,
   audit, and developer convenience. You may read, fork, and modify the
   code for the sole purpose of integrating with the SentiSift API.

3. RESTRICTIONS
   You may not:
   (a) republish the Software under a different name claiming authorship,
   (b) distribute modified versions that pretend to be the official
       client (use a fork name and clearly mark it as unofficial),
   (c) use the Software to implement a competing comment-moderation,
       sentiment-analysis, or content-intelligence API.

